                    <p>To become the most trusted digital healthcare platform that revolutionizes how people access medical consultations, making quality healthcare available to anyone, anywhere, at any time.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="motive-section">
                <h2 style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: 40px;">Our Motive</h2>
                <div class="card" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
                    <p style="font-size: 1.125rem; line-height: 1.7;">
